    <!--Content-Begin-->
    <article>
            <h1>Hvem arbejder med gas i Danmark?</h1>
      <summary>
        <p>
                      
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->

Der er flere organisationer og myndigheder, der arbejder med gas i Danmark. Få en liste over, hvilke aktører der findes og hvilke ansvarsområder de enkelte har.
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->
                            </p>
      </summary>
      <div class="pull-right social-icons">
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl) -->
<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://sik.dk/Forbruger/Gas-vand-og-afloeb/Information-om-gas/Hvem-arbejder-med-gas-i-Danmark" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-facebook-square facebook-brand"></i></a>
<a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=https://sik.dk/Forbruger/Gas-vand-og-afloeb/Information-om-gas/Hvem-arbejder-med-gas-i-Danmark" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter-square twitter-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://sik.dk/Forbruger/Gas-vand-og-afloeb/Information-om-gas/Hvem-arbejder-med-gas-i-Danmark" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-pinterest-square pinterest-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https://sik.dk/Forbruger/Gas-vand-og-afloeb/Information-om-gas/Hvem-arbejder-med-gas-i-Danmark" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-linkedin-square linkedin-brand"></i></a>
<a href="mailto:?subject=Hvem arbejder med gas i Danmark?&body=https://sik.dk/Forbruger/Gas-vand-og-afloeb/Information-om-gas/Hvem-arbejder-med-gas-i-Danmark" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-envelope-o mail-brand"></i></a>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl) -->
</div>
      <br>
      <hr>
        
              
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Hvad gør distributionsselskaberne?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Distributionsselskaberne ejer distributionsnettene og sørger for transport af gas fra det overordnede gastransmissionsnet til forbrugerne. De uddanner samtlige autoriserede vvs-installatørvirksomheder om vigtigheden af korrekt og detaljeret indregulering.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Hvad gør kedelleverandørerne?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
De er ved at udarbejde detaljerede instruktioner om, hvordan deres gaskedler skal indreguleres fremadrettet, og det vil blive sendt ud til alle autoriserede vvs-installatørvirksomheder snarest.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Hvad gør Dansk Gasteknisk Center?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
De udarbejder nye vejledninger, som informerer vvs-installatørerne om vigtigheden af korrekt og omhyggelig indregulering, og så hjælper de gasbranchens aktører med at lokalisere eventuelle problemstillinger i så god tid, at vi forventer, at kunderne ikke vil få driftsproblemer med gas fra Tyskland.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Hvad gør Sikkerhedsstyrelsen?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
De fastlægger blandt andet lovgivningen på gasområdet samt de tilladelige grænser for variationer i gaskvaliteten. Formålet er at fastholde et meget højt sikkerhedsniveau ved anvendelse af naturgas i Danmark.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Hvad gør Energinet.dk?</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Energinet.dk ejer det overordnede gastransmissionsnet i Danmark. Deres opgave er at sørge for at opretholde den overordnede forsyningssikkerhed på gasområdet og at udbygge den overordnede danske gasinfrastruktur. Derudover er det deres opgave at skabe objektive og gennemsigtige betingelser for konkurrence på gasmarkedet og at overvåge, at konkurrencen fungerer.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
      
      
